ass="about-two-right-box"><div class="pbmit-heading-subheading animation-style2"><h4 class="pbmit-subtitle">Overview</h4><h2 class="pbmit-title">Excellence in Formulation, Compliance, and Scale-Up</h2><div class="pbmit-heading-desc">Emnar Pharma was established in 2005. We are leading manufacturers of high-quality generic Active Pharmaceutical Ingredients (APIs), based in Hyderabad, India. We are a part of the Virchow Group of Companies. We are dedicated to providing affordable, reliable, and globally compliant APIs to pharmaceutical companies around the world. With a focus on scalable production, regulatory precision, and deep scientific expertise, we support partners in both regulated and semi-regulated markets.</div><div class="pbmit-heading-desc">Our Vizag Unit 2 API Facility is approved by major global regulatory agencies, including the USFDA, WHO-GMP EDQM, and KFDA. These certifications are a testament to our commitment to quality, safety, and adherence to international manufacturing standards. Additionally, our compliance with CDSCO and other Indian regulatory bodies ensures transparency and efficiency in domestic operations.</div><div class="pbmit-heading-desc">At Emnar, we emphasise cost-effective process development, route-of-synthesis optimisation, and strict impurity profiling, backed by a strong R&amp;D and analytical team. Our API portfolio spans multiple therapeutic segments, and we actively file Drug Master Files (DMFs) to support regulatory submissions for our partners.</div><div class="pbmit-heading-desc">From laboratory-scale innovation to full-scale commercial production, Emnar Pharma is built to serve your API needs with integrity, speed, and reliability.</div><div class="pt-3 mobile-about-list-inside text-center"><a class="pbmit-btn pbmit-btn-blackish-custom" href="contact-us.php"><span class="pbmit-button-content-wrapper"><span class="pbmit-button-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 60 60"><path d="m31 50.979c-.362.007-.